Age of Wonders 4 is a strategy game that takes the best from games like Heroes of Might and Magic and Sid Meier's Civilization. You will play as a ruler who must do everything to ensure that his subjects have a good life, so get ready to expand the borders of your possessions and start wars. But first you need to create a hero and his people, as well as choose a culture, social characteristics and a magic book. All of this will give you starting bonuses, such as improved evasion or plus initiative, that will help you go from the very bottom to greatness. After you decide which map you want to play on, you will find yourself in an open world next to your capital, which at first will be a village with several dozen inhabitants. If you want to try your hand at government, we suggest buying Age of Wonders 4 CD key and leading an army of darkness or light.

The world itself is divided into zones: some are draws and can be joined as soon as you have accumulated enough resources, others belong to neighbors or monsters. At first you will only manage the city and surrounding areas; at this stage you should focus on developing the economy. Build barns, pave roads, dig mines, extract wood and don’t forget to train soldiers. Your lands will constantly be ravaged by squads of monsters until you clear their lair and destroy all the creatures there - this is the local analogue of the barbarian camps from Civilization. When the initial stage is completed, the time will come to get involved in the big game and see if you have enough strength to take over the whole world. The first step on the path to dominance is purchasing Age of Wonders 4 CD key on our trading platform, and the second is smart politics and concluding friendly agreements with allies.

Victory can be achieved in various ways, from military, in which it is enough to simply kill all those who disagree, to magical, where you will need to unlock the fifth tome of magic, and then build a seed, root and heart. The game has a pantheon where all triumphant heroes go; special branches with rewards are available in it, which you can unlock for the points you earn. With each victory you will unlock something new, such as kingdoms or customization items. We offer you to buy Age of Wonders 4 CD key and fight with your own champions, because some heroes from the pantheon may oppose you in the next campaigns.
